          <para styleclass="Popup Box"><text styleclass="Popup Box" translate="true">Alternatively, Edit the X-axis Position of the Blend-Points at the start and end of the segment with the X-axis control in the </text><link displaytype="text" defaultstyle="true" type="topiclink" href="MT-BlendPoint-X-axis-Value" styleclass="Popup Box2" translate="true">Blend-Point Editor</link><text styleclass="Popup Box" translate="true">.</text></para>
